direction: right

title: Token Usage Shape {
  shape: text
  near: top-center
  style.font-size: 28
  style.bold: true
}

naive: Expose every backend schema {
  style.fill: "#FEE2E2"
  style.stroke: "#DC2626"
  style.border-radius: 12

  n1: tools list grows with registry size
  n2: full schemas arrive before the agent chooses
  n3: session cost rises with every new backend
}

gateway: Fixed gateway surface {
  style.fill: "#DCFCE7"
  style.stroke: "#16A34A"
  style.border-radius: 12

  g1: 7 meta-tools stay constant
  g2: brief search and brief inspect are the defaults
  g3: full schema is fetched only for likely calls
}

note: |md
  Savings depend on your registry,
  but the gateway cost grows much more slowly than a full schema dump.
| {
  near: bottom-center
  style.font-size: 13
}

naive -> gateway: discovery narrows before schema expansion
